        <item>
            <title>【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏</title>
            <description>&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;0714&quot;&gt;今天&lt;a class=&quot;s_tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.ithome.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;IT 之家&lt;/a&gt;为大家开箱一款天猫精灵旗下的高端新品 —— 哇哦闺蜜机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;8269&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/4232e5e0-ae98-45f2-a70d-a88b06ec7801.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/4232e5e0-ae98-45f2-a70d-a88b06ec7801.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;墙上的电视中度可信度描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;0&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;ce86&quot;&gt;哇哦闺蜜机整体由三部分构成，顶部的屏幕、中间的支撑杆、以及底部的底座。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;2e6c&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/0159d3d6-cc5c-4ef2-aaf8-c509269d558e.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/0159d3d6-cc5c-4ef2-aaf8-c509269d558e.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;图片包含，物体, 室内, 桌子, 标志描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;1&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;0a9a&quot;&gt;屏幕部分中框和后壳采用了一体化设计，产品轮廓线条流畅自然，并采用了 R 角设计，外观看起来十分友好。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;287a&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/38a42eb2-e60e-4f4c-a6b8-6c51f3a5a3e3.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/38a42eb2-e60e-4f4c-a6b8-6c51f3a5a3e3.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;图片 2&quot; data-weibo=&quot;2&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;880c&quot;&gt;屏幕侧面为对称立体声扬声器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;5500&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/74fb14e5-cd89-4123-a1af-f79071801e53.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/74fb14e5-cd89-4123-a1af-f79071801e53.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;衞生间的门描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;3&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;a575&quot;&gt;屏幕部分有上下 20cm 的升降幅度可调，并且可以横竖旋转 ±90°，上倾斜角可调 25°、下俯角 20°。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;db1a&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/483710fa-4bf8-4b8e-bcb6-b19d8a885e59.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/483710fa-4bf8-4b8e-bcb6-b19d8a885e59.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;穿白色衣服的男人站在门前描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;4&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;fb3c&quot;&gt;屏幕背部配备了 2 枚 USB3.0 接口和一枚 HDMI2.0 接口。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;dc32&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/0a5ee12c-9d95-4de0-8297-11fcd4775a70.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/0a5ee12c-9d95-4de0-8297-11fcd4775a70.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;708&quot; alt=&quot;手机屏幕的截图低可信度描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;5&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;457&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;ef08&quot;&gt;中间的连接杆顶部，采用了晨曦金配色的中置扬声器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;fef7&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/dcdc24ba-8074-463b-8ac4-1bb6bf76df76.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/dcdc24ba-8074-463b-8ac4-1bb6bf76df76.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;杯子里的液体中度可信度描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;6&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;e9bb&quot;&gt;底座部分为配重和低音扬声器，整体机身采用云晓白作为产品主色调，晨曦金作为金属片材的色泽，风格温暖且高级。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;de29&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/8a42e582-391a-4630-94d2-8965fbb3adb1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/8a42e582-391a-4630-94d2-8965fbb3adb1.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;地板上站着中度可信度描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;7&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;574d&quot;&gt;底座与连接杆的固定部分为高亮拉丝工艺的金属片材。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;ab66&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/dc17e41b-705f-4371-806e-2cd79cb5eb06.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/dc17e41b-705f-4371-806e-2cd79cb5eb06.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;图片包含，室内, 桌子, 小, 盘子描述已自动生成&quot; data-weibo=&quot;8&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;96b4&quot;&gt;底座侧面为低音单元的开孔，底部配备了多个静音万向轮。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;29b1&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/431b961e-1bbc-4e5a-9ac5-c95b9d6d23cc.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/431b961e-1bbc-4e5a-9ac5-c95b9d6d23cc.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;1269&quot; h=&quot;715&quot; alt=&quot;图片包含，室内, 桌子, 电脑, 笔记本描述已自动生成&quot; title=&quot;【IT 之家开箱】温润典雅，质感高级。哇哦闺蜜机开箱图赏&quot; width=&quot;1269&quot; height=&quot;462&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;ccfd&quot;&gt;整机与家居风格可以和谐的融为一体。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;4b13&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/987a7d95-a74d-49f4-83fd-aed93631a13d.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/8/987a7d95-a74d-49f4-83fd-aed93631a13d.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_20,x_20,a_0/format,